nodes.text: The Endeavor was a Rebel EF76 Nebulon-B escort frigate that challenged the Imperial frigate Malevolent to an evenly matched duel.

While the occurrence of the space battle depicted in this mission, as well as the participants, is C-Canon, the outcome depends on the actions of the player and is therefore indeterminate. For lack of other canonical information it should be assumed that no lasting effect (such as the destruction of either starship) resulted from the battle.
